Package ai.skymind.pipelines.pipeline.handlers.converter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataPipelineErrorHandler
    Used by JsonArrayConverter implementations to handle logging errors passing in the input data, the exception that happened, and the index of the input.
    JsonArrayConverter
    An interface for converting input json arrays of either arrays of arrays (csvs) or arrays of objects/dictionaries converting the input to either pmml oriented dictionary output or datavec oriented arrow batches.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseJsonArrayConverter  
    JsonArrayMapConverter
    Conversion utility for handling converting arrays of maps to feature vectors for use with inference.
